lead_paragraph: Kirk Nieuwenhuis homered and Matt Garza pitched into the eighth inning, leading the Milwaukee Brewers to a 3-1 victory over the St. Louis Cardinals on Wednesday night, ending a six-game losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Nieuwenhuis Homers, Garza Throws Gem as Brewers Beat Cards
